==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Granivorous
<hw>Gra*niv"o*rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>granum</ets> grain + <ets>vorare</ets> to devour: cf. F.
<ets>granivore</ets>.]</ety> <def>Eating grain; feeding or subsisting on
seeds; <as>as, granivorous birds</as>.</def> <-- seed-eating. not same
as graminivorous? = feeding on grass or the seeds of grass. latter is
for beasts. --> <rj><au>Gay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grannam</ent>⟦br⟧
